01:08:38.157 --> 01:08:41.421
and its impact on cities
like Chicago,

01:08:41.769 --> 01:08:43.944
Kansas City, New York.

01:08:44.162 --> 01:08:46.992
<i>Wherever you had
successful Black baseball,</i>

01:08:47.819 --> 01:08:51.256
