<i>all you've got is a guy
in a uniform.</i>

01:09:27.118 --> 01:09:28.511
<i>And then on the case</i>

01:09:28.685 --> 01:09:30.035
<i>of our old time
Negro ballplayers,</i>

01:09:30.209 --> 01:09:31.993
<i>they were happy doing
what they did.</i>

